/-- **T090 cusp-form specialization of `slash_╬▒_Gamma_p_╬▒_invariant`.**

For a ╬УтВБ(N)-cusp form `f` and any ╬▒ тИИ GL (Fin 2) тДЪ, the slashed function
`тЗСf тИг[k] ╬▒` is invariant under the slash action of `╬У_p(╬▒) тКЖ SL(2, тДд)`.

Direct corollary of `slash_╬▒_Gamma_p_╬▒_invariant` instantiated with the
underlying function `тЗСf`, using `slash_Gamma1_eq` (╬УтВБ(N)-invariance of
the cusp form's underlying function via the SL slash action) plus
`ModularForm.SL_slash` to bridge to the GL slash action via `mapGL тДЭ`.

