open CongruenceSubgroup UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **Phase J тАФ generic SL outer-quotient тЖФ scaled `Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL`
integral bridge.**

For any `╬УтВБ(N)`-invariant `h : тДН тЖТ тДВ` integrable on `Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N`:
```
тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ ╬УтВБ(N), тИл_{q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd} h d╬╝_hyp =
    (slToPslQuot_fiberCard N) тАв тИл_{Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N} h d╬╝_hyp.
```

**Composition of existing PSL machinery (no new measure-theoretic content):**
* `setIntegral_SL_tile_fd_eq_fdo` тАФ converts the SL-tile integral over `fd`
  (closed) to the integral over `fdo` (open); the boundary has measure zero.
* `sum_SL_tile_eq_fiberwise_PSL_tile` тАФ reindexes the SL outer-q sum as a
  PSL inner-q sum weighted by per-fiber cardinalities.
* `slToPslQuot_fiberCard_eq` тАФ the fibers all have cardinality
  `slToPslQuot_fiberCard N` (= 1 for `N тЙд 2`, = 2 for `N тЙе 3`).
* `setIntegral_Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL_eq_sum` тАФ packages the PSL-tile sum
  back into the single integral over `Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N`.

**Use site (Phase J/DSDoubleCosetTileBridge orientation bridge).**  Provides
the missing `Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL` тЖФ outer-quotient SL/╬УтВБ(N) bridge in the
generic form: lifts the `petN_eq_setIntegral_Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL`
identity (currently stated for `petersson f g` only) to any `╬УтВБ(N)`-invariant
integrand `h`, with the universal `slToPslQuot_fiberCard N` factor.

This lemma extracts the inline `gen_SL_fd_sum_eq` block from the proof of
`sum_setIntegral_GL2_shift` (line 1920) into a reusable top-level
identity.  The `(slToPslQuot_fiberCard N)` weight on the RHS is **not
optional**: for `N тЙе 3` the SL coset space is a 2-fold cover of the
PSL/imageGamma1_PSL coset space (since `-I тИЙ ╬УтВБ(N)` distinguishes
SL-cosets `[q]` and `[-q]` that project to the same PSL-coset), so the
SL outer sum genuinely overcounts the PSL fundamental-domain integral
by exactly `slToPslQuot_fiberCard N`. -/
theorem setIntegral_Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL_eq_SL_outer_q_sum
    (h : тДН тЖТ тДВ)
    (h_inv : тИА ╬│ тИИ Gamma1 N, тИА ╧Д : тДН, h (╬│ тАв ╧Д) = h ╧Д)
    (h_int : IntegrableOn h (Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N) ╬╝_hyp) :
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      тИл ╧Д in (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ тАв (fd : Set тДН), h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp =
    (slToPslQuot_fiberCard N) тАв тИл ╧Д in Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N, h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp := by
  classical
  calc тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
          тИл ╧Д in (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ тАв (fd : Set тДН), h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp
      = тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
          тИл ╧Д in (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ тАв (fdo : Set тДН), h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp :=
        Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => setIntegral_SL_tile_fd_eq_fdo h q
    _ = тИС q' : PSL(2, тДд) тз╕ imageGamma1_PSL N,
          (Finset.univ.filter (fun q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N =>
            slToPslQuot q = q')).card тАв
            тИл ╧Д in ((q'.out : PSL(2, тДд)))тБ╗┬╣ тАв (fdo : Set тДН), h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp :=
        sum_SL_tile_eq_fiberwise_PSL_tile h h_inv
    _ = (slToPslQuot_fiberCard N) тАв тИС q' : PSL(2, тДд) тз╕ imageGamma1_PSL N,
          тИл ╧Д in ((q'.out : PSL(2, тДд)))тБ╗┬╣ тАв (fdo : Set тДН), h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp := by
        rw [Finset.smul_sum]
        refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q' _ => ?_
        congr 1
        convert slToPslQuot_fiberCard_eq q' using 2
        congr
    _ = (slToPslQuot_fiberCard N) тАв тИл ╧Д in Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N, h ╧Д тИВ╬╝_hyp := by
        rw [тЖР setIntegral_Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL_eq_sum h h_int]

