* Integrability on the ╬УтВБ(N)-FD: `integrableOn_petersson_Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL`.

**Use site (Phase K orientation bridge).**  Provides the cleanest typed form
of the SL/╬УтВБ(N) outer-q тЖФ scaled `Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL` integral identity for
the Petersson integrand actually consumed downstream by `petN` and the
