-- The lemma `peterssonInner_fd_eq_smul_fd` was REMOVED on 2026-04-08:
-- It claimed `тИл_{╬│тБ╗┬╣┬╖fd} petersson(f,g) = тИл_{fd} petersson(f,g)` for ╬│ тИИ SLтВВ(тДд),
