/-! ### GLтВВтБ║ coset adjoint lifted to petN

The symmetric Hecke adjoint (DS Theorem 5.5.3 core):
`petN(T_p f, g) = petN(тЯиpтЯйf, T_p g)`.

This is the symmetric form of the adjoint identity, equivalent to
`petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_unsymm` via `diamondOp_petersson_unitary`.

Proof sketch (DS ┬з5.5): for each T_p coset representative `╬▒_b тИИ GLтВВтБ║(тДЪ)` and each
`╬УтВБ(N)`-coset `[q]`, apply `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint` to get:
```
