    = тИл_{╬▒_bтАвfd} petersson k (fтИгqтБ╗┬╣) ((gтИгqтБ╗┬╣)тИгadj(╬▒_b)) d╬╝
```
Then factor `adj(╬▒_b) = ╬│тВБ ┬╖ ╬▒_{╧Г(b)} ┬╖ ╬│тВА` where `╬│тВБ тИИ ╬УтВБ(N)`,
`╧Г` permutes the indices, and `╬│тВА = adjointGamma0Rep` represents `тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣`.
After `╬УтВБ(N)`-tile reindexing and the permutation `╧Г`, the sum reconstructs
as `petN(тЯиpтЯйf, T_p g)`.

