/-- **T024 aggregate per-╬▒ slash-adjoint at the ╬УтВБ(N)-FD level**.

Sum-level aggregation of `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` over the
`SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N` quotient: the per-q-per-╬▒ slash-adjoint identity,
summed over q, collapses (via `peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint`)
to a single Petersson integral over the ╬▓-shifted ╬УтВБ(N) fundamental
domain `тЛГ_q (╬▓ ┬╖ mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd`.

**Mathematical content (sum-level absorbed-RHS route).**  This provides
content (A) of the per-╬▒ residual reduction described in
`petN_LHS_dist_eq_RHS_absorbed_from_two_residuals`'s docstring: the
per-╬▒ aggregate slash-adjoint at the ╬УтВБ(N)-FD level. Combined with the
matrix-coset bijection `peterssonAdj ╬▒ тЖФ ╬▒^*` modulo ╬УтВБ(N) (content
(B)), it discharges the per-╬▒ residual via Hecke double-coset matching.

**Inputs.**  Caller supplies:
* `h╬▓ : 0 < ╬▓.det.val` (╬▓ has positive determinant);
* `hd : Pairwise AEDisjoint` of the ╬▓-shifted ╬УтВБ(N) tile family
  (from existing AE-disjoint helpers like
  `aedisjoint_glMap_M_infty_T_p_upper`,
  `aedisjoint_glMap_T_p_upper_pair_fd_per_q` for specific ╬▓);
* `hm : NullMeasurable` of each tile;
* `hint : IntegrableOn` of `petersson k F (G тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓)` on
  the union.

**Use site (DS 5.5.2(b)).**  Apply with ╬▓ = `glMap M_тИЮ` for the M_тИЮ
residual reduction or ╬▓ = `glMap T_p_upper(b)` for the upper-b residual
reduction; supply the AE-disjoint and integrability hypotheses from the
existing per-tile helpers landed in this file. -/
theorem peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_coset_aggregate
    (╬▓ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) (h╬▓ : 0 < ╬▓.det.val)
    (F G : UpperHalfPlane тЖТ тДВ)
    (hd : Pairwise (fun (qтВБ qтВВ : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N) =>
      AEDisjoint ╬╝_hyp
        ((╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (qтВБ.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН))
        ((╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (qтВВ.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв fd)))
    (hm : тИА q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      NullMeasurableSet
        ((╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)) ╬╝_hyp)
    (hint : IntegrableOn (fun ╧Д => petersson k F (G тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓) ╧Д)
      (тЛГ q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        (╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)) ╬╝_hyp) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (F тИг[k] (╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
        (G тИг[k] (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) =
    peterssonInner k
      (тЛГ q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        (╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН))
      F (G тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓) := by
  rw [show (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (F тИг[k] (╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (G тИг[k] (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) =
      тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k
          ((╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН))
          F (G тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓) from by
    refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
    rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset (k := k) ╬▓ h╬▓
      (q.out : SL(2, тДд)) F G, тЖР mul_smul]]
  exact (peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint
    (fun q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N =>
      (╬▓ * (mapGL тДЭ (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тАв (fd : Set тДН))
    hm hd F (G тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓) hint).symm

