/-- **T106 right-slash M_тИЮ adjoint coset identity**: per-`q` M_тИЮ-summand
transformation for the Hecke adjoint.

Composes `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` (at ╬▓ = glMap M_тИЮ) with
`peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq` to rewrite the `g`-side adjoint-slash in a
clean form suitable for the right-slash T205 closure path. The resulting
RHS integrand is `g тИг[k] (glMap T_p_upper(0) * mapGL тДЭ ╧Г_pтБ╗┬╣)`, which on
a cusp form further simplifies via the matrix identity `T_p_upper(0) ┬╖ ╧Г_pтБ╗┬╣
= p ┬╖ M_тИЮтБ╗┬╣` (not used here тАФ kept in this compiled form for flexibility). -/
theorem peterssonInner_M_infty_slash_adjoint_coset
    (N p : тДХ) [NeZero N] (hp : 0 < p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (q : SL(2, тДд)) (f g : тДН тЖТ тДВ) :
    peterssonInner k fd
        (f тИг[k] ((glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
          (mapGL тДЭ qтБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
        (g тИг[k] (mapGL тДЭ qтБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) =
