/-- **T205-d-SYMM M_тИЮ-tile set equivalence**:
`(T_p_lower ┬╖ M_тИЮ) тАв S = mapGL тДЭ M_infty_Gamma1_factor тАв S` for any `S : Set тДН`. -/
