/-- **T128 per-q `M_тИЮ` slash-adjoint reduction** (M_тИЮ analog of
`peterssonInner_slash_adj_T_p_upper_q_summand_eq`).

For each `q : SL(2, тДд)`, the per-q `M_тИЮ` summand of `petN(T_p f) g` reduces via
`peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` (╬▓ = `glMap M_тИЮ`) + the T106 M_тИЮ adjoint
bridge (`slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0`)
to a `peterssonInner` on a shifted tile with the SAME b-independent g-slot
`(тЗСg тИг glMap T_p_upper(0)) тИг mapGL ╬│тВА` used by the upper-family analog.

This completes the per-q Option (Fin p)-family slash-adjoint reduction to a
uniform target g-slot, enabling the `peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_constantRHS`
collapse across the full p+1 family {T_p_upper(b) : b тИИ Fin p} тИк {M_тИЮ}. -/
private lemma peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (q : SL(2, тДд)) (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (тЗСf тИг[k] ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
          (mapGL тДЭ qтБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
        (тЗСg тИг[k] (mapGL тДЭ qтБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) =
    peterssonInner k ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
        ((mapGL тДЭ qтБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
      тЗСf
      ((тЗСg тИг[k] (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тИг[k]
