  rw [slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0
    p hp hpN g]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 DS `p+1` family per-q split collapse**
(split-family strategy, avoiding any GL-valued `Option (Fin p) тЖТ GL` definition).

For fixed `q : SL(2, тДд)` and ╬УтВБ(N)-cusp forms `f, g`, the sum of the `M_тИЮ`
slash-adjoint summand with the upper-family `тИС_b` summand rewrites to the
