open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 DS p+1 family per-q combined split-union**: builds on
`peterssonInner_ds_p_plus_one_family_union_collapse_per_q_split` by further
collapsing the `тИС_b` upper summand into a single `peterssonInner` over the
upper-family union-tile via `peterssonInner_T_p_upper_family_union_collapse_per_q`,
while keeping the `M_тИЮ` tile separate from the upper-family union
(domain split as M_тИЮ tile + upper-union tile, no Option-valued GL matching).

This is the fixed-`q` deliverable directly consumable at the LHS per-q of
`petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form`.

**Form conversion**: the per-b rewrite produces tiles in `╬▒ тАв (mapGL qтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd)`
form; the upper-family union-collapse expects `(╬▒ * mapGL qтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd` form.
