/-- **T128 RHS branch normalization (upper family)**: rewrites
`тЗС(тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg) тИг[k] (glMap T_p_upper(b) * mapGL qтБ╗┬╣)` in combined GL(2, тДЭ) form
