b-independent `тЗСf тИг[k] glMap T_p_upper(0)`, with raw `тЗСg` in the third slot
and domain `glMap T_p_lower тАв mapGL (q * ╬│тБ╗┬╣)тБ╗┬╣ тАв fd`.

