                M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)тБ╗┬╣)тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
            (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
        ((тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
