open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T205-d M_тИЮ master-identity reverse** (CuspForm f-slot version):
`f тИг T_p_lower ┬╖ ╬│ ┬╖ qтБ╗┬╣ = тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйf тИг M_тИЮ ┬╖ qтБ╗┬╣` where
