applied to `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйf` and bridging via diamond cancellation `тЯиuтЯйтИШтЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй = id`.

Used in the M_тИЮ-branch tile-shifted reduction of the LHS-distributed sum
in `SigmaQPermResidual_M_infty`. -/
private lemma slash_T_p_lower_factor_eq_diamond_inv_slash_M_infty
