**Mathematical reference.**  DiamondтАУShurman, *A First Course in Modular
Forms*, Prop. 5.5.2(b) and Thm. 5.5.3; Miyake ┬з4.5. -/
private theorem petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_of_LHS_bridge
