/-- **T024 M_тИЮ branch slot-2 unfactor reduction.**

Applies `slash_M_infty_eq_diamond_slash_T_p_lower_factor.symm` per-`q` to
convert the **absorbed** RHS form's slot-2
`тЯиuтЯйg тИг[k] (T_p_lower * mapGL ╬│_X * mapGL ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣)` back to the **pre-factored**
form `g тИг[k] (M_тИЮ * mapGL ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣)`.  This reduces the M_тИЮ branch hypothesis
to a **strictly smaller** equality where slot-2 is the canonical M_тИЮ form
(no `тЯиuтЯй` shift, no T_p_lower factorization).

After this reduction, the remaining algebraic gap is:

  тИС_q  peterssonInner k fd  (f тИг[k] T_p_lower * mapGL ╬│_X * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
                              (g тИг[k] mapGL ╬│тВА * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
  =
  тИС_q  peterssonInner k fd  (f тИг[k] mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
                              (g тИг[k] M_тИЮ * mapGL ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣)

The remaining gap is the **slash-adjoint exchange** (det-`p` element across
slots) plus the Q-reindex `q тЖФ ╧Гq` mismatch on slot-2 vs slot-1.  The exchange
shifts the integration domain by the det-`p` element, and the ╧Г-reindex
absorbs the resulting per-`q` shift via `Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0` at the sum
level.

**Mathematical reference.** DiamondтАУShurman, *A First Course in Modular
Forms*, Prop. 5.5.2(b); Miyake ┬з4.5. -/
private theorem M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) g) тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  congr 1
  exact (slash_M_infty_eq_diamond_slash_T_p_lower_factor p hp hpN g
    (Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
      ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out).symm

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 M_тИЮ branch LHS ╧Г-reindex.**

Reusable sum-level reindex lemma on the LHS-distributed M_тИЮ branch shape:
relabels the dummy `q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N` summation index via the
`Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 ╬│тВА` bijection (╬│тВА = `adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN`),
moving the indexing from `q.outтБ╗┬╣` to `(╧Г q).outтБ╗┬╣` throughout the M_тИЮ
branch summand.

**Proof.**  Pure `Equiv.sum_comp` on ╧Г тАФ mathematically content-free,
mathematical equivalent of relabeling a dummy variable in a finite sum.

**Role.**  Composes with `M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2` to align the
slot-2 indexing of the LHS-distributed and pre-factored RHS forms; the
remaining residual is the slot-1 q тЖФ ╧Гq mismatch and the slash-adjoint
exchange of the det-`p` `T_p_lower * ╬│_X` factor across slots. -/
private theorem M_infty_branch_LHS_sigma_reindex
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  set ╧Г : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N тЙГ SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N :=
    Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
      ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property
  exact (╧Г.sum_comp _).symm

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 M_тИЮ branch LHS normalize-to-diamond.**

Per-`q` normalization of the LHS-distributed M_тИЮ summand to a `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй`-shifted
form, applying the user-route steps:

* Slot-1: `slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon.symm` at `q.out`,
  converting `f тИг[k] (T_p_lower * mapGL ╬│_X * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)` to
  `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйf тИг[k] (M_тИЮ * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)`.
* Slot-2: `diamondOpCusp_eq` + `adjointGamma0Rep_units` + `SlashAction.slash_mul`
  identifying `g тИг[k] (mapGL ╬│тВА * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) = тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg тИг[k] mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣`.

After this normalization, the M_тИЮ branch LHS sum has the canonical shape
expected by `peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq` (with `f` and
`g` replaced by their `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй`-shifts). -/
private theorem M_infty_branch_LHS_normalize_to_diamond
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f) тИг[k]
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) := by
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  -- Slot-2 helper: `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg = g тИг[k] mapGL ╬│тВА` via `diamondOpCusp_eq` + `adjointGamma0Rep_units`.
  have h_diamond : (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) :
      UpperHalfPlane тЖТ тДВ) =
      тЗСg тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) := by
    show тЗС(diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) = _
    rw [diamondOpCusp_eq k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) (adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN)]
    rfl
  -- Slot-1: rewrite via slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon.symm.
  rw [show (тЗСf тИг[k]
      ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
        ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
            M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
        ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) =
    (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f) тИг[k]
      ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
        ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
    from (slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon p hp hpN
      (q.out : SL(2, тДд)) f).symm]
  -- Slot-2: identify `g тИг[k] (mapGL ╬│тВА * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) = тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg тИг[k] mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣`
  -- via `slash_mul` + `h_diamond.symm`.
  rw [show (тЗСg тИг[k]
      (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
        ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) =
      (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
        ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
          (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))
    from by rw [SlashAction.slash_mul, тЖР h_diamond]]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 sum-level M_тИЮ branch slash-adjoint reindex (prefactored RHS).**

The SMO-critical sum-level bridge relating the LHS-distributed M_тИЮ branch
form to the prefactored RHS M_тИЮ branch form (the form produced by composing
`M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2` on the absorbed RHS).  Proves:

  тИС_q  peterssonInner k fd  (f тИг[k] T_p_lower * mapGL ╬│_X * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
                              (g тИг[k] mapGL ╬│тВА * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
  =
  тИС_q  peterssonInner k fd  (f тИг[k] mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)
                              (g тИг[k] M_тИЮ * mapGL ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣)

where ╧Гq = `Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 ╬│тВА q`, ╬│_X = `gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor 0 *
M_infty_Gamma1_factor 0`, ╬│тВА = `adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN`.

**Route.**  Composes:

1. `M_infty_branch_LHS_normalize_to_diamond`: LHS sum тЖТ `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйf тИг M_тИЮ * q.outтБ╗┬╣` /
   `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg тИг q.outтБ╗┬╣` form (`slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon` +
   `diamondOpCusp_eq` + `adjointGamma0Rep_units` + `slash_mul`).
2. `peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq` per-`q` via `Finset.sum_congr`:
   `peterssonInner k fd (F тИг M_тИЮ * qтБ╗┬╣) (G тИг qтБ╗┬╣) = peterssonInner k (M_тИЮ тАв qтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd) F ((G тИг T_p_upper(0)) тИг ╬│тВА)`
   (with `F = тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйf`, `G = тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg`).
3. `h_tile_shift_to_prefactored`: explicit named **sum-level Q-reindex absorption
   hypothesis** equating the M_тИЮ-tile-shifted-domain form (with `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй`-shifted f
   and g) to the prefactored fd-form (with original f and g, ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣ on slot-2).
   This is the irreducible analytic content of DS 5.5.2(b) at the sum level тАФ
   the per-q domain shift `(M_тИЮ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd` is absorbed by relabeling
   `q тЖж ╧Г q` in the sum, and the `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй`-shifts on f and g cancel via
   `petN_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex` symmetry.

**Composition with `M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2`** discharges the
`h_M_infty_branch` hypothesis required by `petN_LHS_dist_eq_RHS_absorbed_from_branches`. -/
private theorem M_infty_branch_sum_slash_adjoint_reindex_prefactored
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k)
    (h_tile_shift_to_prefactored :
      (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
              (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
                (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
            тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)
            ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
              (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тИг[k]
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))))) =
      тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
            (тЗСg тИг[k]
              ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
                ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                  ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                    ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                    (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                    SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  -- Step 1: Normalize LHS to тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй-shifted form.
  rw [M_infty_branch_LHS_normalize_to_diamond p hp hpN f g]
  -- Step 2: Per-q apply `peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq`.
  rw [show (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f) тИг[k]
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
          ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
              (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
          тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
            (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))))
    from Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ =>
      peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq p hp hpN
        (q.out : SL(2, тДд))
        (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)
        (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g)]
  -- Step 3: Apply the explicit Q-reindex absorption hypothesis.
  exact h_tile_shift_to_prefactored

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 M_тИЮ branch hypothesis discharger.**

Composes `M_infty_branch_sum_slash_adjoint_reindex_prefactored` (LHS-distributed
тЖФ prefactored RHS via Q-reindex absorption) with
`M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2.symm` (prefactored RHS тЖФ absorbed RHS, via
`slash_M_infty_eq_diamond_slash_T_p_lower_factor`) to produce **exactly** the
`h_M_infty_branch` hypothesis required by
`petN_LHS_dist_eq_RHS_absorbed_from_branches`.

The single remaining open hypothesis is `h_tile_shift_to_prefactored` тАФ the
sum-level Q-reindex absorption that converts the per-q M_тИЮ-tile-shifted
domain (`(M_тИЮ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd` with `тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯй`-shifted f, g) to the prefactored
fd-form (with `╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣` on slot-2). This is the irreducible analytic
content of DS 5.5.2(b) at the sum level. -/
private theorem M_infty_branch_hypothesis_via_sum_chain
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k)
    (h_tile_shift_to_prefactored :
      (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k
            ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
              (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
                (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
            тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)
            ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g) тИг[k]
              (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тИг[k]
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))))) =
      тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
            (тЗСg тИг[k]
              ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
                ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                  ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                    ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                    (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                    SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          (тЗСg тИг[k]
            (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) g) тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                  M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, тДд))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  rw [M_infty_branch_sum_slash_adjoint_reindex_prefactored p hp hpN f g
    h_tile_shift_to_prefactored,
    тЖР M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2 p hp hpN f g]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 T_p_upper(b) branch slot-2 unfactor reduction.**

T_p_upper(b)-family analog of `M_infty_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2`. Per-`q`,
per-`b`: applies `slash_T_p_upper_eq_diamond_slash_T_p_lower_factor.symm` to
convert the absorbed RHS slot-2 `тЯиuтЯйg тИг[k] T_p_lower * ╬│_b * ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣` back
to the prefactored `g тИг[k] T_p_upper(b) * ╧Гq.outтБ╗┬╣`. -/
private theorem T_p_upper_branch_RHS_unfactor_slot2
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    (тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      тИС b тИИ Finset.range p,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (тЗСf тИг[k] ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            (q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) g) тИг[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)) *
              ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
