/-- **T024 sum-level slash-adjoint coset reduction for M_тИЮ slot-swap.**

Per-`q` application of `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` over the
quotient sum: for each `q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N`, swaps the slash on
slot-1 (carrying `glMap M_тИЮ`) with `peterssonAdj` action on slot-2,
shifting `fd` by `M_тИЮ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣`.

