/-- **LHS-aggregate-as-tile-form** (Step 2 (in progress) of T205-d-SYMM chain,
2026-05-11). Expresses `petN(T_p f, g)` as a sum over `(q, ╬▓)` of
`╬▓`-translated tile integrals over `fd`, where `╬▓` ranges over the Hecke
representatives `{glMap M_тИЮ} тИк {glMap T_p_upper(b)}_{b<p}` and `q` ranges over
`SL(2, тДд) тз╕ ╬УтВБ(N)`.

Combines:
- `petN_T_p_heckeT_p_LHS_sum_distributed` (existing LHS-distributed sum form)
- `peterssonInner_LHS_distributed_summand_to_tile_form` (per-`(╬▓, q)` ADJ-WRAPPER
  consumer, new in this beastmode pass)
- `glMap_M_infty_det_pos` (M_тИЮ has det `p > 0`)
- `glMap_T_p_upper_det_pos` (T_p_upper(b) has det `p > 0`)

This is the analytic-side LHS rewrite that the next step of T205-d-ADJ-CORR
consumes: aggregating these tile integrals via the FD-transport theorem
(T205-d-API-1) gives an integral over a finite-index subgroup FD which then
re-tiles a ╬УтВБ(N)-FD. -/
theorem petN_heckeT_p_LHS_as_tile_aggregate
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      (peterssonInner k
          ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
            (((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : SL(2, тДд)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
          тЗСf
          ((тЗСg : тДН тЖТ тДВ) тИг[k]
            peterssonAdj (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))
        + тИС b тИИ Finset.range p,
            peterssonInner k
              ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
                (((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : SL(2, тДд)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
              тЗСf
              ((тЗСg : тДН тЖТ тДВ) тИг[k]
                peterssonAdj (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  rw [petN_T_p_heckeT_p_LHS_sum_distributed p hp hpN f g]
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  congr 1
  ┬╖ exact peterssonInner_LHS_distributed_summand_to_tile_form q
      (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
      (glMap_M_infty_det_pos N p hp.pos hpN) f g
  ┬╖ refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun b _ => ?_
    exact peterssonInner_LHS_distributed_summand_to_tile_form q
      (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
      (glMap_T_p_upper_det_pos p hp.pos b) f g

