/-- **LHS-aggregate-as-tile-form with per-╬▓ g-slot identifications**.

Refinement of `petN_heckeT_p_LHS_as_tile_aggregate` that applies the per-╬▓
adjugate slash identifications to the g-slot:

- For ╬▓ = `glMap T_p_upper(b)`:
  `тЗСg тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓ = тЗСg тИг[k] glMap T_p_lower` (independent of `b`!)
  via `slash_peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower`.

- For ╬▓ = `glMap M_тИЮ`:
  `peterssonAdj ╬▓ = glMap T_p_upper(0) * mapGL тДЭ ╧Г_pтБ╗┬╣`, so
  `тЗСg тИг[k] peterssonAdj ╬▓ = (тЗСg тИг[k] glMap T_p_upper(0)) тИг[k] mapGL тДЭ ╧Г_pтБ╗┬╣`
  via `peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq` + `SlashAction.slash_mul`.

The T_p_upper(b) branch summands now have a `b`-INDEPENDENT integrand
`petersson k тЗСf (тЗСg тИг[k] glMap T_p_lower)`. Summing over `b` therefore
collapses to integration over the union `тЛГ_b T_p_upper(b) тАв (q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd)`,
which is the upper branch of the T_p Hecke double-coset tile family at `q`. -/
theorem petN_heckeT_p_LHS_as_tile_aggregate_g_slot_simplified
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k) :
    petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
    тИС q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      (peterssonInner k
          ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
            (((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : SL(2, тДд)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
          тЗСf
          (((тЗСg : тДН тЖТ тДВ) тИг[k] (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              (sigma_p_specific N p hp.pos hpN)тБ╗┬╣))
        + тИС b тИИ Finset.range p,
            peterssonInner k
              ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв
                (((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣ : SL(2, тДд)) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
              тЗСf
              ((тЗСg : тДН тЖТ тДВ) тИг[k]
                (glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  rw [petN_heckeT_p_LHS_as_tile_aggregate p hp hpN f g]
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  congr 1
  ┬╖ -- M_тИЮ branch: rewrite peterssonAdj (glMap M_тИЮ) via the explicit factoring.
    rw [peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq N p hp.pos hpN, SlashAction.slash_mul]
  ┬╖ -- T_p_upper(b) branch: rewrite per-b adjugate slash to T_p_lower.
    refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun b _ => ?_
    rw [slash_peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower p hp hpN b g]

