/-- **T205-d ADJ-CORR step 11.9**: per-`q` ╧Г_p-aligned form of the uniform
╧Г_p Q-permutation template.

For each `q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ ╬УтВБ(N)`, the per-tile identity
```
