**natural setting** for the ╧Г_p Q-permutation argument: both slots have
the same slash factor `peterssonAdj M`, so the ╧Г_p Q-permutation on
`SL(2,тДд) тз╕ ╬УтВБ(N)` acts symmetrically on the diamond-twisted slots
(f, тЯиuтБ╗┬╣тЯйg) тЖФ (тЯиuтЯйf, тЯиuтЯйg).  This matches the reviewer's prescription
that the ╧Г_p Q-permutation lives on the finite correspondence /
transposed quotient data (see expert review 2026-05-11). -/
