`h_per_tile` into the **M_тИЮ branch** of
`heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance` (i.e. `h_canon.1`), via
`peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint`.

**Genuinely smaller geometric fact.**  The per-tile hypothesis
`h_per_tile q` is the slot-swap identity `(fтИгM_тИЮ, g) = (f, gтИгM_тИЮ)`
restricted to a *single* SL-tile `(mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd`, whereas the
aggregate hypothesis (the M_тИЮ branch of `heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance`)
