open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 / T205 strict reducer: per-tile slot-swap from per-q FD-form balance.**

Pulls back the per-tile slot-swap identity (over the SL-tile
`(mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd`) to the per-q FD-form balance (over `fd`) via
`peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash`.  This pushes one layer deeper
than `heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_╬▒_branch_from_per_tile_balance`:
the SL-tile domain is converted to fd via the SL change-of-variables,
folding the integration shift into the integrand slashes.

**Strictly smaller hypothesis.** The per-q FD-form balance
`h_per_q_fd q` is a single equality of integrals over a *fixed* domain
(`fd`), with the SL-tile shift absorbed into the slash composition
`╬▒ * (mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)` on the f-slot and `mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣` alone on the
g-slot.  The per-tile form has the *shifted* domain `(mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd`
but a simpler integrand pair (`f тИг ╬▒, g`).

**Why this is a real reduction, not repackaging.** The proof body
applies the SL-pullback identity `peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash`
on each side of the per-tile equation, then folds the resulting
nested slashes `(F тИг ╬▒) тИг (mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) = F тИг (╬▒ * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)`
via `SlashAction.slash_mul`.  Both steps are non-trivial helpers, not
mere renaming.

**Proof structure.**
1. `intro q`.
2. Apply `peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash` on each side (LHS and RHS):
   converts `peterssonInner k ((mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) тАв fd) F G` to
   `peterssonInner k fd (F тИг mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣) (G тИг mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)`.
3. Fold the slot-1 slashes `((F тИг ╬▒) тИг mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)` to
   `F тИг (╬▒ * mapGL q.outтБ╗┬╣)` via `тЖР SlashAction.slash_mul`.
4. Apply `h_per_q_fd q`. -/
private theorem heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_╬▒_branch_per_tile_from_per_q_fd_balance
    (╬▒ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k)
    (h_per_q_fd : тИА q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)) тИг[k]
            (╬▒ * ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) =
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))
          ((тЗСg) тИг[k]
            (╬▒ * ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))) :
    тИА q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
          (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв (fd : Set тДН))
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)) тИг[k] ╬▒)
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g)) =
        peterssonInner k
