open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 / T205 strict reducer: per-q FD-form balance from shifted-tile
diamond/slot swap (single named genuine analytic content).**

Reduces the per-q FD-form ╬▒-slot-swap (consumed by
`╬▒_branch_per_tile_from_per_q_fd_balance`) to a **single named genuine
analytic identity**: the **shifted-tile diamond/slot swap residual**

  `peterssonInner k (╬▒ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd) (тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣f) ((тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣g) тИг peterssonAdj ╬▒)
    = peterssonInner k (╬▒ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd) ((тЯиpтЯйf) тИг peterssonAdj ╬▒) g`

тАФ a per-`q` Petersson identity over the *same* shifted-tile domain
`╬▒ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd`, with the diamond `тЯиpтЯй` тЖФ `тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣` swap and the slot
swap (slot-1 тЖФ slot-2) absorbing each other across `peterssonAdj ╬▒`.

**Why this is the irreducible analytic core (manager hint #2:
"diamond-twisted slash-invariance theorem strong enough to move ╬▒
between Petersson slots over fd").**  Both sides have IDENTICAL slash
compositions on slot-i where ╬▒ appears (just `peterssonAdj ╬▒`), with
the only difference being:
* slot-1: `тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣f` (LHS) vs `(тЯиpтЯйf) тИг peterssonAdj ╬▒` (RHS) тАФ diamond-twist + slash-by-╬▒ swap;
* slot-2: `(тЯиpтЯйтБ╗┬╣g) тИг peterssonAdj ╬▒` (LHS) vs `g` (RHS) тАФ diamond-twist + slash-by-╬▒ swap.

The `q.outтБ╗┬╣` factor of the original slash composition `╬▒ ┬╖ q.outтБ╗┬╣` has
been absorbed into the integration domain via SL change-of-variables;
the genuine per-q content thereby reduces to the diamond-twisted
slot-swap of the Petersson kernel for `╬▒` against itself, evaluated on
the SL-tile.

**Proof structure.**
1. `intro q`.
2. Apply `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` (╬▓ := ╬▒, q := q.out) on
   LHS_target: the slash composition `(╬▒ ┬╖ q.outтБ╗┬╣)` is absorbed via
   change-of-variables to give an integral over `╬▒ тАв q.outтБ╗┬╣ тАв fd` with
   slot-2 carrying `peterssonAdj ╬▒`.
3. Apply `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right` (╬▓ := ╬▒, q := q.out)
   on RHS_target: the slash composition `(╬▒ ┬╖ q.outтБ╗┬╣)` on the
   slot-2 of `g` is absorbed, putting `peterssonAdj ╬▒` on slot-1.
4. Apply `h_shifted q` to close the residual.

This is uniform in ╬▒, so the same theorem covers both M_тИЮ and
T_p_upper(b) Hecke representatives. -/
private theorem heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_╬▒_branch_per_q_fd_from_shifted_tile_diamond_swap
    (╬▒ : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) (h╬▒ : 0 < ╬▒.det.val)
    (p : тДХ) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL тДЭ)) k)
    (h_shifted : тИА q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
          (╬▒ тАв (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
          (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f))
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g)) тИг[k]
            peterssonAdj ╬▒) =
      peterssonInner k
          (╬▒ тАв (((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ) тАв (fd : Set тДН)))
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) тИг[k]
            peterssonAdj ╬▒)
          тЗСg) :
    тИА q : SL(2, тДд) тз╕ Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f)) тИг[k]
            (╬▒ * ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)))
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)) =
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) тИг[k]
            ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))
          ((тЗСg) тИг[k]
            (╬▒ * ((mapGL тДЭ : SL(2, тДд) тЖТ* GL (Fin 2) тДЭ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, тДд))тБ╗┬╣) : GL (Fin 2) тДЭ))) := by
  intro q
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset (k := k) ╬▒ h╬▒ ((q.out : SL(2, тДд)))
        (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ f))
        (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)тБ╗┬╣ g))]
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right (k := k) ╬▒ h╬▒ ((q.out : SL(2, тДд)))
        (тЗС(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f))
        (тЗСg)]
  exact h_shifted q

